18
00:03:10,762 --> 00:03:14,907
Well, then the next thing I do will be
totally "un-me" and completely out of character!

19
00:03:25,471 --> 00:03:28,487
I tripped and fell!

20
00:03:28,512 --> 00:03:30,973
That is so something she would do.

21
00:03:31,606 --> 00:03:34,253
Yup. Seems about right.

22
00:03:55,978 --> 00:03:57,146
<i>Daifuku</i> !

23
00:03:57,171 --> 00:03:59,103
Come and get your <i>daifuku</i> here!

24
00:04:00,138 --> 00:04:01,310
Sorry, but...

25
00:04:01,884 --> 00:04:04,469
