It's raining!

122
00:11:27,304 --> 00:11:29,043
I gotta go bring in the laundry!

123
00:11:31,371 --> 00:11:33,002
Hey! That's the wrong way!

124
00:11:33,994 --> 00:11:34,675
Huh?

125
00:11:47,826 --> 00:11:48,303
There!

126
00:11:50,054 --> 00:11:53,607
Yay!

127
00:11:55,899 --> 00:11:56,579
Uh...

128
00:11:56,804 --> 00:11:58,062
Looks like it's wet already.

129
00:11:58,109 --> 00:11:59,369
You should still bring it in!

130
00:12:02,826 --> 00:12:05,536
Hakase, Sakamoto, I'm home!

131
00:12:06,224 --> 00:12:07,904
It started pouring out of nowhere,

132
00:12:07,929 --> 00:12:09,488
so I hope you were able to get the laundry

133
00:12:09,513 --> 00:12:11,248
before it got too wet.

134
00:12:15,569 --> 00:12:18,244
It's not my fault! Sakamoto told me to bring it in!

135
00:12:19,102 --> 00:12:20,144
I'm tellin' ya!

136
00:12:20,215 --> 00:12:23,282
It was all the kitty's idea. He
was the one that made me do it!

137
00:12:24,702 --> 00:12:26,530
So what you're saying is,

138
00:12:26,648 --> 00:12:30,533
you knocked the laundry over while
Sakamoto was making you bring it in?

139
00:12:30,637 --> 00:12:33,860
No, he specifically told me
to take the clothes and just...

140
00:12:33,887 --> 00:12:35,237
throw them all on the ground.

141
00:12:35,262 --> 00:12:36,252
I did not!

142
00:12:36,465 --> 00:12:37,732
Way to blindside me.

143
00:12:37,786 --> 00:12:39,696
Don't blame someone else for your messes, kid!

144
00:12:39,721 --> 00:12:40,906
But you said to!

145
00:12:40,931 --> 00:12:42,696
I never told you to throw things on the ground!

146
00:12:42,721 --> 00:12:43,369
Did, too!

147
00:12:43,393 --> 00:12:44,262
I did not!

148
00:12:44,306 --> 00:12:45,009
Did, too!

149
00:12:45,033 --> 00:12:45,874
I did not!

