00:12:46,042 --> 00:12:46,742
Did, too!

151
00:12:46,766 --> 00:12:47,620
I did not!

152
00:12:47,708 --> 00:12:48,315
Did, too!

153
00:12:48,339 --> 00:12:49,208
I did not!

154
00:12:49,346 --> 00:12:49,990
Did, too!

155
00:12:50,014 --> 00:12:50,736
I did not!

156
00:12:50,762 --> 00:12:52,176
I wish you weren't a liar!

157
00:12:52,221 --> 00:12:53,170
I'm what?!

158
00:12:54,167 --> 00:12:55,000
Nano.

159
00:12:55,202 --> 00:12:57,965
Why don't we just blame this whole thing on Sakamoto?

160
00:12:58,194 --> 00:12:59,005
That okay?

161
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:00,385
That is not okay, brat!

162
00:13:00,429 --> 00:13:01,425
No big deal.

163
00:13:01,592 --> 00:13:04,520
I just gotta wash that laundry
again and it'll be good as new.

164
00:13:04,545 --> 00:13:06,265
Oh! Good point!

165
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,395
Guess that's true.

166
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:11,895
But, I'll never get the time I spend on it back.

167
00:13:12,791 --> 00:13:15,564
As punishment, neither of you
will be getting dinner tonight.

168
00:13:15,596 --> 00:13:16,777
Aww.

169
00:13:16,802 --> 00:13:18,196
Dammit. I didn't do anything wrong!

170
00:13:18,279 --> 00:13:20,168
But it was only Sakamoto's fault!

171
00:13:20,201 --> 00:13:21,696
See? He said so himself!

172
00:13:21,721 --> 00:13:24,138
He confessed! So you can blame him!

173
00:13:24,874 --> 00:13:25,760
All right, then.

174
00:13:26,181 --> 00:13:28,261
Since he owned up to his mistakes,

175
00:13:28,877 --> 00:13:30,953
the only one that doesn't get dinner is you.

176
00:13:32,701 --> 00:13:34,362
Wait! I wanna take some of the blame!

177
00:13:34,387 --> 00:13:35,821
And I can own up to my mistakes, too!

178
00:13:35,846 --> 00:13:37,196
Like how I was the one who tried to

179
00:13:37,221 --> 00:13:38,705
bring in the laundry in the first place

180
00:13:38,730 --> 00:13:40,755
and accidentally knocked it over and got it all wet...

181
00:13:44,585 --> 00:13:45,376
Ta-da!

182
00:13:45,435 --> 00:13:48,110
We'll be having special rice omelets for dinner!

183
00:13:48,262 --> 00:13:49,430
Wow!

184
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:51,134
The eggs were on sale today!

185
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:53,617
Wait. I thought I wasn't allowed to have dinner.

186
00:13:54,283 --> 00:13:55,257
Yeah, you're right!

187
00:13:55,565 --> 00:13:57,544
I completely forgot about that!

188
00:13:59,689 --> 00:14:02,111
Well, um... then...

189
00:14:02,472 --> 00:14:05,321
I guess I can let you have the rice omelette for tonight!

190
00:14:05,346 --> 00:14:06,762
Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay!

191
00:14:06,787 --> 00:14:08,880
But tomorrow, you get nothing!

