00:20:07,048 --> 00:20:08,878
Unleashing that move in a friendly match?

269
00:20:08,939 --> 00:20:10,335
He's completely insane!

270
00:20:10,902 --> 00:20:12,166
I have no choice.

271
00:20:12,191 --> 00:20:14,381
I can't just stand by and do nothing.

272
00:20:14,997 --> 00:20:17,420
Father, the fated day has arrived.

273
00:20:22,421 --> 00:20:24,637
In the name of all that is just,

274
00:20:24,932 --> 00:20:27,452
shed thy light and become a star!

275
00:20:28,279 --> 00:20:31,460
Ogi Forbidden Referee School! Secret Technique!

276
00:20:34,237 --> 00:20:36,277
Ogi Star!

277
00:20:49,857 --> 00:20:50,646
This is it!

278
00:20:50,825 --> 00:20:53,347
A final love for all!

279
00:20:59,441 --> 00:21:00,574
You're pretty good.

280
00:21:02,609 --> 00:21:04,172
Hey, thanks. You, too.

281
00:21:07,829 --> 00:21:09,882
What the heck?

282
00:21:09,994 --> 00:21:12,984
I kinda just started this little club on a whim.

283
00:21:13,629 --> 00:21:14,805
But now...

284
00:21:15,607 --> 00:21:18,145
...it's gotten crazier than I could've imagined!

285
00:23:10,248 --> 00:23:10,922
Huh?

286
00:23:15,773 --> 00:23:16,815
Huh?

287
00:23:20,364 --> 00:23:23,047
I break down when no one can see me.

288
00:23:26,792 --> 00:23:29,154
Step on me all you'd like, but I'll never break!

289
00:23:29,179 --> 00:23:30,838
That's right, it's me, Clay!

290
00:23:30,862 --> 00:23:32,498
I can be molded into anything!

291
00:23:32,556 --> 00:23:35,497
But today, I shall take the form
best suited to battle the children!

292
00:23:35,576 --> 00:23:38,409
The next episode of <i>My Ordinary Life</i> is Episode 20!

293
00:23:38,505 --> 00:23:40,609
All right, kids, bring it on!

